==Mandarin==
{{zh-forms|[[宁]][[波]]|[[寧波]]}}
===Etymology===
From: [[宁]] tranquil; peaceful + [[波]] waves
===Proper noun===
{{cmn-proper|s|pin=Níngbō|pint=ning2bo1|tra=寧波|sim=宁波|rs=宀02}}

# [[Ningbo]] (a port city in [[Zhejiang]] Province, China)

===Usage notes===
*[[宁]] is either nìng (ning4) or níng (ning2), depending on the meaning.  In this case, the meaning is '''peaceful''' or '''tranquil''' (''not'' "would rather"), so it should be níng (ning2).   

